{"tid":591670,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得08歐國杯係近10年最好睇的國家隊杯賽","createTime":"2018-03-13T17:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T18:15:22.000Z","uid":8919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e06e0a5b3529fdae3cc2692cd2d49f80ab307293","tid":591670,"uid":8919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T17:58:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OARqQyKEy_g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOARqQyKEy_g&d=AuF%2BR4E1NNtI17gjFGCCJwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=4851065b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OARqQyKEy_g</a><br />\n好多經典野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n韋拿好似第一場戴帽、小學雞彈起、Cech派膠被反cup、法國意大利爭出線、波歷克遠射幫德國出線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n淘汰賽好幾場都好好睇：德對提子、西班牙對意大利、俄羅斯對荷蘭、決賽費托一箭定江山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後啲國家隊比賽都好似好悶咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d82f4ed46d1dfa3d5520c487456cc3fd42af9f","tid":591670,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T18:01:57.000Z","msg":"2012歐國杯好悶"},{"pid":"b316632370f387a360a842d5e2c091b6e8be5f37","tid":591670,"uid":8919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41d82f4ed46d1dfa3d5520c487456cc3fd42af9f","tid":591670,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T18:01:57.000Z","msg":"2012歐國杯好悶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T18:15:22.000Z","msg":"係，只係記得決賽意大利比西班牙炒4粒同四強意對德巴神入兩球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}